The paper deals with axiomatization and metric extension of bisimilarity distance on Markov chains, which involves concepts from logic, artificial intelligence, programming languages, data structures, and mathematics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.PL (Programming Languages), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.MA (Mathematical Software).
